com.example.arontandrix

Class TutorialEdgeBasedInitialization

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.arontandrix.TutorialEdgeBasedInitialization

  • public class TutorialEdgeBasedInitialization
extends java.lang.Object
    Starts the AR application. First it searches for the 3D object in the pictures from the camera. When the object is found it is tracked and its position is shown in screen coordinates.
    Author:
    metaio, Andrej
